title: Pilot.ReplyD
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Saira, I found this $CLUE. Can you tell me anything about it?
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Pilot>>
<<Portrait|Pilot_neutral>>
That's $CREWMATE's, I've seen them around with it.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Thanks, Saira.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Pilot>>
<<Portrait|Pilot_neutral>>
See you around.
<</Textbox>>
